extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.ChildOf<org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Augmentable<PortModErrorNotification>, TransactionMetadata, TransactionAware, NodeErrorReference, BaseNodeErrorNotification, ErrorMessage, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Notification
    Model for ofp_error-Type=7 - Port mod request failed.

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module node-error
    (Source path: META-INF/yang/node-errors.yang): 

     notification port-mod-error-notification {
     description
         "Model for ofp_error-Type=7 - Port mod request failed.";
     leaf type {
         type error-type;
     }
     leaf code {
         type uint16;
     }
     leaf data {
         type string;
     }
     leaf transaction-id {
         type transaction-id;
     }
     leaf transaction-uri {
         type uri;
     }
     leaf node {
         type node-ref;
     }
     choice object-reference {
         case flow-ref {
             leaf flow-ref {
                 type flow-ref;
             }
         }
         case group-ref {
             leaf group-ref {
                 type group-ref;
             }
         }
         case meter-ref {
             leaf meter-ref {
                 type meter-ref;
             }
         }
     }
     uses transaction-metadata;
     uses transaction-aware;
     uses node-error-reference;
     uses base-node-error-notification;
     uses error-message;
     status CURRENT;
 }
